sequenceDiagram
    actor Agency
    actor ASM
    actor RA as RA / Finance
    participant FAP as FAP Portal
    participant DB as FAP Database
    participant MuleSoft as MuleSoft ESB
    participant SAP as SAP ERP
    participant WH as Warehouse System
    rect rgb(10, 30, 60)
        Note over SAP, DB: FLOW 1 — PO Sync from SAP to FAP Portal (Scheduled Job)
        SAP->>MuleSoft: PO created with Supplier mapping
        MuleSoft->>FAP: Push {poNumber, vendorCode}
        FAP->>DB: Upsert PurchaseOrders table {poNumber, vendorCode}
    end
    rect rgb(10, 30, 60)
        Note over Agency, DB: FLOW 1B — Agency Views Their POs
        Agency->>FAP: View My POs
        FAP->>DB: SELECT FROM PurchaseOrders WHERE vendorCode = agency.vendorCode
        DB-->>FAP: Matching PO records
        FAP-->>Agency: List of PO Numbers only
    end
    rect rgb(20, 10, 50)
        Note over WH, DB: FLOW 2 — Warehouse Territory Sync (Scheduled Job — data stored in FAP DB)
        WH->>FAP: Sync territory master data
        FAP->>DB: Upsert TerritoryMapping table {state, asmId, asmName, asmEmail, region, dealerName}
    end
    rect rgb(20, 10, 50)
        Note over Agency, ASM: FLOW 2B — Agency Creates FAP Submission and ASM is Auto-Assigned
        Agency->>FAP: Create FAP submission {poNumber, activityDetails}
        FAP->>DB: Lookup TerritoryMapping by State or VendorCode
        Note over FAP, DB: ⚠ Confirm with team — is ASM lookup by State or by VendorCode?
        DB-->>FAP: {asmId, asmName, asmEmail, region, dealerName}
        FAP->>DB: Save submission — assignedAsmId set, status = Submitted
        FAP->>ASM: New FAP assigned to you — In-App + Email + Teams notification
    end
    rect rgb(10, 40, 10)
        Note over Agency, SAP: FLOW 3 — AI Validation After Submission
        FAP->>FAP: DocumentAgent — classify and extract documents
        FAP->>FAP: ValidationAgent — run 43 validation rules
        FAP->>FAP: RecommendationAgent — generate APPROVE / REVIEW / REJECT
        FAP->>FAP: ConfidenceScoreService — calculate weighted score
        FAP->>ASM: Notify — Submission ready for your review
    end
    rect rgb(40, 10, 10)
        Note over ASM, SAP: FLOW 4 — ASM Real-Time PO Amount Check (ASM-Triggered)
        ASM->>FAP: Opens submission — reviews AI summary and recommendation
        ASM->>FAP: Clicks Check PO Amount button
        FAP->>MuleSoft: GET /api/sap/validate-po {poNumber, invoiceAmount}
        MuleSoft->>SAP: Fetch PO approved amount and balance
        SAP-->>MuleSoft: {poApprovedAmount, poRemainingBalance, poStatus}
        MuleSoft-->>FAP: {approvedAmount, remaining, status}
        FAP-->>ASM: PO Amount check result displayed on screen
        Note over ASM, FAP: No hard block — ASM can override and Approve or Reject based on their judgement
    end
    rect rgb(5, 35, 20)
        Note over ASM, RA: FLOW 5A — Approval Path
        ASM->>FAP: Approve submission with comments
        FAP->>DB: Record ASM approval + timestamp, status = ASM Approved
        FAP->>RA: Notify — FAP ready for Finance review — In-App + Email + Teams
        RA->>FAP: Review submission with ASM remarks visible
        RA->>FAP: Approve
        FAP->>DB: Record RA approval + timestamp, status = RA Approved
        FAP->>MuleSoft: POST /api/sap/trigger-payment {poNumber, invoiceAmount, vendorCode}
        MuleSoft->>SAP: Create Service Entry and Payment Posting
        SAP-->>MuleSoft: {sapPaymentDocNumber, status: posted}
        MuleSoft-->>FAP: {paymentDocNumber, postedAt}
        FAP->>Agency: Notify — Payment initiated — In-App + Email
    end
    rect rgb(50, 15, 5)
        Note over RA, Agency: FLOW 5B — Rejection Path (RA Rejects)
        RA->>FAP: Reject submission with reason
        FAP->>DB: Record RA rejection + reason, status = Rejected
        FAP->>Agency: Notify — Submission rejected by Finance — reason included — In-App + Email + Teams
        Agency->>FAP: Open submission — review rejection reason
        Agency->>FAP: Modify documents or amounts and resubmit
        FAP->>DB: New submission version created, status = Submitted
        FAP->>ASM: Notify — Resubmission received for your review — In-App + Email + Teams
        Note over Agency, ASM: Flow restarts from FLOW 3 — AI Validation runs again on resubmission
    end